# Pipeline layout

| Stage | Module |
|-------|--------|
| Load | `io.dataset.load_image` |
| Preprocess | `detection.preprocess.preprocess_image` |
| Masks | `detection.masks.build_candidate_masks` |
| Candidates | `detection.candidates.find_candidate_boxes` (pass `text_source=prep.gray`) |
| Score | `detection.scoring.score_candidate` |
| Post | `detection.postprocess.postprocess_boxes` |
| API | `detection.detector.detect_name_labels` |
| Batch | `runtime.pipeline.process_dataset` |

Tune thresholds in `detection.config.DetectionConfig`. Package root: `src/pdiseg/`. See `docs/src/ARCHITECTURE.md`.

After changing scoring/postprocess, run `tests/test_run.py` and `tests/test_detector_validation.py`.
